{
  "texts": [
    "The selection of these conditions was guided by their prevalence and significance in public health.",
    "Then, the queries were translated by the first author (a native speaker of Jordanian Arabic) into the Jordanian dialect and by the second author (a native speaker of Tunisian Arabic) into the Tunisian dialect.",
    "The same ten queries were prompted on both ChatGPT models to be used as a reference of the content generated.",
    "Specificity of Used PromptsThe study employed a strict approach to prompting each ChatGPT model.",
    "The prompts were used as exact questions without any feedback to ensure consistency."
  ]
}